1- Download Java and set Java_Home in environmental variables 

2- Download Android STUDIO : https://developer.android.com/studio/index.html
3- Set Android_Home Environmental variables path to SDK location and include bin folder paths in PATH variable 
4- configure Virtual device/Emulator

5- Download Node.js : https://nodejs.org/en/download/
6- Set Node_Home Environmental variables path
7- Set npm Environmental variables path 
8- Download Appium Server from Node
